mutation {
  createPeopleMutation(input: {

    	mass: "90", 		
      hairColor:"BLACK",

      gender: "MALE",

  })
    {
    people {
      name
      height
      hairColor
      skinColor
      eyeColor
      mass    
      gender
      birthYear
      id
    }
  }
}
